sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice as Alice (Client)
    participant Server as Server (HTTPS)
    participant Bob as Bob (Client)
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: LOGIN PHASE
    
    Alice->>Server: POST /login<br/>{username, password}
    Server->>Server: Verify password with bcrypt
    Server->>Server: Generate session token
    Server-->>Alice: {session_token}
    Alice->>Alice: Store session token
    
    Bob->>Server: POST /login<br/>{username, password}
    Server->>Server: Verify password with bcrypt
    Server->>Server: Generate session token
    Server-->>Bob: {session_token}
    Bob->>Bob: Store session token